  "local_port": 44360,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What I have to do after I catch pokemon in pokemon go?",
  "response": "After you catch a Pok\u00e9mon in Pok\u00e9mon GO, there are several steps you can take to maximize your gameplay experience:\n\n1. **Assess the Pok\u00e9mon's IVs**: Use the in-game appraisal system to check your Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s IVs (individual values). This will help you determine if it's worth investing resources into powering it up.\n\n2. **Power Up**: If the Pok\u00e9mon has good stats, you might consider using Stardust and candies to power it up, increasing its CP (Combat Power).\n\n3. **Evolve**: If your Pok\u00e9mon can evolve and you have enough candies, you might choose to evolve it to improve its stats and get access to new moves.\n\n4. **Learn New Moves**: Use Technical Machines (TMs) or Elite TMs to teach your Pok\u00e9mon new moves that might be more effective in battles.\n\n5. **Transfer**: If you have multiple copies of the same Pok\u00e9mon and don\u2019t need all of them, you might transfer the weaker ones to Professor Willow to get candies in return that can be used to power up or evolve other Pok\u00e9mon of the same species.\n\n6. **Trade**: Trade your Pok\u00e9mon with friends to try to get better IVs, a different species, or to complete your Pok\u00e9dex. Trades also grant bonus candies, especially for Pok\u00e9mon that are far away.\n\n7. **Use in Battles**: Your newly caught Pok\u00e9mon can be used in various battles, including gym battles, raid battles, and player-versus-player (PvP) battles in the Battle League.\n\n8. **Set as Buddy**: Set your Pok\u00e9mon as your buddy to earn candies, find souvenirs, and unlock more features of the buddy system.\n\n9. **Check for Special Tasks**: Sometimes caught Pok\u00e9mon fulfill special research tasks that earn you rewards.\n\n10. **Customize Your Pok\u00e9mon**: If you want, you can give your Pok\u00e9mon a nickname and take snapshots with it.\n\nThese steps will help you build a stronger team, earn rewards, and progress in the game more effectively.",
